title: It's "Tap," not "Tab"
text: It's "Tap," not "Tab" People are all confused over a misspelling in the instructions. It's "Tap," not "Tab." You either Tap on an emoji then tap the green "Whats app" button at the bottom. Or you extend Tap an emoji and it opens up in WhatsApp. I agree about changing the black background to white. Otherwise it works just fine.
